OL,3,CHow MP Naz Shah overcame 'toughest
OL,4,Cbeginnings' to represent her community
OL,6,FNaz Shah still remembers the first
OL,7,Ftime she saw her Dad abusing her Mum -
OL,8,Fshe was just five-years-old and living
OL,9,Fin Bradford.
OL,11,FShe tells me her mum Zoora "had a long
OL,12,Fplait and he had her plait in his hand
OL,13,Fand I run up the stairs, went to the
OL,14,Fneighbours, and I called the
OL,15,Fneighbours to come and stop him from
OL,16,Fbeating her.
OL,18,F"That was one of my very first
OL,19,Fmemories."
OL,26,@sD@\OU
