OL,3,CHow MP Naz Shah overcame 'toughest
OL,4,Cbeginnings' to represent her community
OL,6,FHers is a story of adversity and
OL,7,Fsurvival - a story she has now written
OL,8,Fdown on paper for her book 'Honoured'.
OL,10,FIt tells of her rise from the toughest
OL,11,Fbeginnings to the heart of power,
OL,12,Frepresenting Bradford West as an MP
OL,13,Fsince 2015.
OL,15,FHer dad eventually ran off with a 16-
OL,16,Fyear-old neighbour, her mum and her
OL,17,Fsiblings were left with next to
OL,18,Fnothing.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1772806277
OL,3,CHow MP Naz Shah overcame 'toughest
OL,4,Cbeginnings' to represent her community
OL,6,FBut then a man she knew only as
OL,7,F"Uncle" Azam entered their life,
OL,8,Foffering the family help.
OL,10,FNaz says her Mum was a "23-year-old
OL,11,Fwoman without the support of family -
OL,12,Fin a very vulnerable situation living
OL,13,Fin unsecure accommodation and the
OL,14,Foffer of security must have seemed
OL,15,Flike my knight in shining armour."
OL,17,FBut Azam turned out to be no hero.
OL,19,FNaz later learnt that he had been
OL,20,Fabusing her mother, raping her, and
OL,21,Fsending other men to also assault her.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@GO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
