PN,36708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1772806277
OL,3,CHow MP Naz Shah overcame 'toughest
OL,4,Cbeginnings' to represent her community
OL,6,F"When you've experienced being
OL,7,Fhomeless, when you've experienced
OL,8,Fsleeping on a mattress, when you've
OL,9,Fexperienced trying to kill yourself
OL,10,Fbecause you couldn't cope anymore,
OL,11,Fbecause you're in so much despair...
OL,12,Fwhen a constituent reaches out, when
OL,13,Fservices aren't working, I can feel
OL,14,Fthat pain."
OL,16,FIf you've been affected by any issues
OL,17,Fin our news programmes, these links to
OL,18,Findependent charities and
OL,19,Forganisations may be able to provide
OL,20,Fsome advice and support.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G8/8
